FILTER ( strEnds(str(?resource), 'content') &&  strStarts(str(?resource), 'http://gillingham.library.ualberta.ca:8080/fedora/rest/prod/44') ) . ?resource ?predicate ?object . FILTER ( !contains(str(?predicate), 'http://www.iana.org/assignments/relation/') && !contains(str(?predicate), 'http://fedora.info/definitions/v4/repository#hasFixityService')  && !contains(str(?predicate), 'http://fedora.info/definitions/v4/repository#hasParent') && str(?object)!='' )  .
